{% liquid
  assign heading = section.settings.heading
%}

<div class="section spacing-style color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <div class="section-inner page-width">
    <div class="sustainability-content">
      {% if heading != blank %}
        <h1 class="heading-1">{{ heading }}</h1>
      {% endif %}

      <p class="sustainability-intro">At JACKEETA, sustainability isn't an afterthought – it's woven into every decision we make. We're committed to creating beautiful clothing that respects both people and planet.</p>

      <div class="sustainability-sections">
        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">01</div>
          <h2>RESPONSIBLE SOURCING</h2>
          <p>We carefully select our materials from certified suppliers who share our values. Our natural fibers are sourced from mills that prioritize environmental responsibility and fair labor practices.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Organic cotton from GOTS-certified farms</li>
            <li>Wool from mulesing-free farms</li>
            <li>Linen from European flax fields</li>
            <li>Recycled materials where appropriate</li>
            <li>Traceable supply chains</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">02</div>
          <h2>QUALITY OVER QUANTITY</h2>
          <p>The most sustainable garment is one that lasts. We design with longevity in mind, creating timeless pieces that transcend trends and can be worn for years.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Durable construction techniques</li>
            <li>Reinforced seams and stress points</li>
            <li>Timeless designs that don't date</li>
            <li>Easy to repair and maintain</li>
            <li>Classic silhouettes that endure</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">03</div>
          <h2>ETHICAL PRODUCTION</h2>
          <p>We partner with factories that uphold the highest standards of worker welfare. Every person involved in making our garments deserves fair wages, safe conditions, and respect.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Fair wage commitments</li>
            <li>Safe working environments</li>
            <li>Regular factory audits</li>
            <li>Long-term partnerships</li>
            <li>No child or forced labor</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">04</div>
          <h2>REDUCING WASTE</h2>
          <p>We're constantly working to minimize waste throughout our operations, from pattern cutting to packaging.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Efficient pattern making to reduce fabric waste</li>
            <li>Minimal, recyclable packaging</li>
            <li>Responsible inventory management</li>
            <li>Upcycling fabric scraps</li>
            <li>Plastic-free where possible</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">05</div>
          <h2>TRANSPARENCY</h2>
          <p>We believe you have a right to know where your clothes come from and how they're made. We're committed to openness about our practices and continuous improvement.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Clear material information</li>
            <li>Factory location disclosure</li>
            <li>Honest about our challenges</li>
            <li>Regular sustainability reporting</li>
            <li>Open to customer questions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sustainability-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-number">06</div>
          <h2>CIRCULARITY</h2>
          <p>We're exploring ways to extend the life of our garments and keep them out of landfills.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Care instructions to extend garment life</li>
            <li>Repair guides and services</li>
            <li>Take-back programs (coming soon)</li>
            <li>Resale platform (in development)</li>
            <li>Recycling partnerships</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sustainability-commitment">
        <h2>OUR COMMITMENT</h2>
        <p>Sustainability is a journey, not a destination. We're not perfect, but we're dedicated to continuous improvement. We regularly assess our practices, listen to our community, and seek better ways to operate.</p>
        <p>Every purchase you make supports these efforts. Together, we can build a more sustainable fashion industry – one thoughtfully made garment at a time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sustainability-contact">
        <h3>QUESTIONS ABOUT OUR PRACTICES?</h3>
        <p>We welcome your inquiries about our sustainability efforts.</p>
        <div class="button-wrapper">
          <a href="/pages/contact" class="button button--secondary">CONTACT US</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .sustainability-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .heading-1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sustainability-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .sustainability-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 64px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar {
    position: relative;
  }

  .pillar-number {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar > p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sustainability-pillar li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .sustainability-commitment {
    padding: 48px;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .sustainability-commitment h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sustainability-commitment p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sustainability-commitment p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .sustainability-contact {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 48px 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .sustainability-contact h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .sustainability-contact p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .button-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .sustainability-sections {
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .sustainability-pillar ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sustainability-commitment {
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .sustainability-contact {
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Sustainability",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Sustainability"
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Sustainability"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
